                  </hi>. I am employed by Messrs. Candy &amp; Co.—on 12th September, the prisoner came to my department and selected goods to the amount of 65<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I handed the prisoner over to Mr. Hayes.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
